Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Big MAC saves New York
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b03z8hrw
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 15 Jun 1975
Big MAC - the new Municipal Assistance Corporation - to take control of New York City's troubled finances. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less